AI Chat
AI Chat is an AI chatbot that writes text. You can use it to write stories, messages, or programming code. You can use the AI chatbot as a virtual tutor in almost any subject.

To install Nginx on your web-01 server and configure it to meet the requirements, you can follow these steps in a Bash script:

    Update the package list and upgrade existing packages.
    Install Nginx.
    Configure Nginx to listen on port 80.
    Create an HTML file with the "Hello World!" content.
    Configure Nginx to serve the HTML file at the root.

Here's the Bash script to automate these steps:

#!/bin/bash

# Update the package list and upgrade existing packages
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade -y

# Install Nginx
sudo apt-get install nginx -y

# Configure Nginx to listen on port 80
sudo mv /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/default /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/default.bak
cat << EOF > /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/default
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name localhost;
    root /var/www/html;
    index index.html;
    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
    }
}
EOF

# Create an HTML file with the "Hello World!" content
echo 'Hello World!' > /var/www/html/index.html

# Restart Nginx
sudo service nginx reload
